bugetc
_fd_

#include <jelio.h>

Reads one character from filedescripor _fd_.
The data from filedescriptor _fd_ is buffered internally. The buffer can be freed by a call to buclose(_fd_).

Returns the character read.
If EOF was reached -1 is returned.
If a memory allocation error was encountered -2 is returned.

